{"tid":210333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微胖界瑜珈女神爆紅","createTime":"2017-04-20T23:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T10:47:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":37,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6e23d80be05cf4fe926f02bb7b8258225fb833","tid":210333,"uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-04-20/1024/20170420003688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-04-20%2F1024%2F20170420003688.jpg&h=44ce8fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微胖界瑜珈女神爆紅！「胸器」快讓緊身衣撐爆了 (圖/翻攝Seulmin IG)<br />\n<br />\n日前一名「瑜珈女神」在網路上爆紅，並非她長得特別艷麗，或是做了什麼樣高難度瑜珈動作，而是靠著清秀臉蛋及凹凸有致性感身材贏得網友注意，甚至還有對岸網友稱該名正妹為「瑜珈女神」、「微胖界女神」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-04-20/1024/20170420003689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-04-20%2F1024%2F20170420003689.jpg&h=88648f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「瑜珈女神」是來自於南韓的網路美女Seulmin。(圖/翻攝Seulmin IG)<br />\n<br />\n這名女神在大陸爆紅，但其實她真實身分卻是來自於南韓的網路美女Seulmin，熱愛瑜珈的她時常在網路上分享健身照，只見Seulmin穿著一身亮色系緊身衣褲，凹凸有致的身材展露無遺，胸前兩粒幾乎快要把上衣撐爆。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-04-20/1024/20170420003692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-04-20%2F1024%2F20170420003692.jpg&h=c2758747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSeulmin雖然沒有一般模特兒般纖細的身材，但她前凸後翹性感模樣卻一點也不輸給超模，肉感比例相當完美。(圖/翻攝Seulmin IG)<br />\n<br />\nSeulmin與其他網路正妹不同的地方在於，就算沒有直接露出「胸器」，但緊身的瑜珈服卻讓她「雄偉」的上圍更加引人注目，讓不少男網友看後直噴鼻血。<br />\n<br />\nSeulmin雖然沒有一般模特兒般纖細的身材，但她前凸後翹性感模樣卻一點也不輸給超模，肉感比例相當完美，讓人好想將臉深埋在她身上，引發男性網友無限想像，讓兩岸網友全都為之瘋狂，紛紛封她為「微胖界女神」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-04-20/656/20170420003698.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-04-20%2F656%2F20170420003698.jpg&h=e9c4fb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSeulmin被兩岸網友封為「微胖界女神」。(圖/翻攝Seulmin IG)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170420003638-260808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20170420003638-260808&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=65960a20\" target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170420003638-260808</a>"},{"pid":"02fd124c8189f1ca3887a1ec77e9eff436bd2aee","tid":210333,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 波大唷"},{"pid":"ce618abbfa8b8796a72c009878ed78a5eb1645cb","tid":210333,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:58:24.000Z","msg":"支那女人除左做雞仲可以做乜"},{"pid":"6b405d4eeb7d4923d58698beeebb6d91ddc980e5","tid":210333,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703053985b121b65e85183e4429c4fd31aa033e0","tid":210333,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n極品呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f506f757a5b2ccae2c5d138860077349f6600a","tid":210333,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那女人除左做雞仲可以做乜</blockquote><br />\n屌原來泡菜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599f152791c91577b75c9e625dc07cdfdf6da7a4","tid":210333,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T23:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那女人除左做雞仲可以做乜</blockquote><br />\n有得屌你屌唔屌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"